Zen Programming Language


>>> What Zen is:
----------------
Zen is a featherweight yet powerful language designed for both embedding
and stand-alone purposes. Zen is compact and requires little resource.
It's written in ANSI C, and compiles on most common platforms.
It has many useful features like dynamic typing and garbage collection.
For a detailed description of Zen, refer to the documents.
Zen is very young and still under rapid development, please keep a close eye on the
next release for more exciting new features.

>>> How do I install Zen:
-------------------------
Zen can be easily built on different platforms.
For more information, please refer to the INSTALL notes in the same directory as this file.

>>> How can I contact the authors:
----------------------------------
Zen's authors welcome any constructive suggestions, criticisms, and bug reports.
You can reach us on:
